OL,3,C'It is daunting': Parents say children
OL,4,Cwith autism have limited childhoods
OL,6,FThe Guernsey Sports Commission ran a
OL,7,Fpilot scheme whereby five children
OL,8,Fwith complex needs participated in a
OL,9,F90-minute sports class at Le Rondin
OL,10,Fschool today (Friday 5 April).
OL,12,FAnthea Roue's daughter Evie has autism
OL,13,Fand complex verbal needs, whilst her
OL,14,Fson is neurotypical.
OL,16,FShe highlighted a disparity in
OL,17,Fprovision for her children, saying:
OL,18,F"As he's getting older the gap is
OL,19,Fbecoming more and more obvious.
