OL,3,C'It is daunting': Parents say children
OL,4,Cwith autism have limited childhoods
OL,6,F"The activities available for our
OL,7,Fyounger child are there and we can
OL,8,Fbook him into something, but for our
OL,9,Fdaughter they are not there.
OL,11,F"We have to find them. We have to
OL,12,Fcreate them. Waking up in the morning
OL,13,Fand knowing there is nothing planned
OL,14,Ffor her can be a long and daunting day.
