OL,3,C'It is daunting': Parents say children
OL,4,Cwith autism have limited childhoods
OL,6,FSimilarly, Marc Winn has a six-year-
OL,7,Fold autistic daughter called Emie and
OL,8,Fsays since her diagnosis it has been
OL,9,Fhard on the whole family.
OL,11,FHe even compared her Emie's childhood
OL,12,Fto lockdown, saying: "The last four
OL,13,Fyears have been probably the most
OL,14,Fchallenging experience of my life, you
OL,15,Fend up isolated from your existing
OL,16,Ffriends.
OL,18,F"You end up isolated from most of the
OL,19,Fcommunity in terms of getting access
OL,20,Fto it and it's become a tough time.
