OL,3,C'It is daunting': Parents say children
OL,4,Cwith autism have limited childhoods
OL,6,F"Most families remember what lockdown
OL,7,Fwas like and during the holidays and
OL,8,Fweekend it can be very similar to what
OL,9,Flockdown felt like.
OL,11,F"We all have a feeling of what
OL,12,Flockdown felt like but that can last
OL,13,Ffor a whole childhood."
OL,15,FA statement from Guernsey's Education
OL,16,FCommittee says: "We are pleased to see
OL,17,Fthe work the Sports Commission are
OL,18,Fdoing.
